            "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Protect your Heart </h2><br>In this psychological, emotional experience you have to protect your heart from getting harmed. <br>Doing so will evolve a short but impactful story around yourself and the protagonist. <br>In order to protect your heart and soul from being damaged you have the ability to move a shield and therefore to shield yourself from incoming attacks and obstacles. <br>The situation, however, will take an unexpected turn…<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Understand one's Feelings </h2><br>Loathing Heart is a very experimental game which is designed to put you in the shoes of someone else and to give you a deeper inside of their mind and thoughts. <br>The storytelling is supported by the main game mechanic which changes slightly yet significantly over time… <br>Besides a lot of other things game contains critics of our general social system and raises the questions of how we treat other people and in how far we create our own enemies.<br>The game also contains 3 acts. With every act changes the pace, general mood, and design of the whole environment.<br>The further you get the more you will understand what is going on…<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Think and Discuss </h2><br>Be warned, quite some of the actual content is written very abstractly and is open to interpretation.",
